REPUBLIC OF KENYA

IN THE MATTER OF THE OATHS AND STATUTORY DECLARATIONS ACT

(CAP 15 OF THE LAWS OF KENYA)

AFFIDAVIT

I, {full_name}, of Kenyan Identity Card Number {id_number} and of Post Office Box Number {post_box} in the Republic of Kenya, do hereby make oath and state as follows: -

1. THAT I am a {gender} adult of sound mind, competent to make and swear this affidavit.

2. THAT {statement_1}

3. THAT {statement_2}

4. THAT {statement_3}

5. THAT {statement_4}

6. THAT {statement_5}

7. THAT what is deponed herein above is true to the best of my knowledge, information, and belief.

SWORN at {location} by the said

{full_name}

DEPONENT

This {day} day of {month} {year}

BEFORE ME

COMMISSIONER FOR OATHS
